            <section class="doc-section">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>
                    Day 3 was about writing more "functional" JavaScript and expanding the REST API
                    We also looked at how URL's are structured, how to serve HTML with Express, and learning about XSS (Cross-Site Scripting).
                </p>
